OL,3,CNigel Farage vows to clean up Reform's
OL,4,Cimage post election
OL,6,FNigel Farage told ITV News Political
OL,7,FCorrespondent Harry Horton that he
OL,8,Fwould be 'ruthless' in cleaning the
OL,9,Fimage of Reform up.
OL,11,FNigel Farage has pledged to clean up
OL,12,FReform's image after his party managed
OL,13,Fto shake up the Westminster scene and
OL,14,Fgain more MPs at the General Election.
OL,16,FThe Reform leader was among four
OL,17,Fcandidates in the party - including
OL,18,FLee Anderson and Richard Tice - to win
OL,19,Ftheir respective seats.
